title: What is this Webinar about?
content: This webinar is an exclusive opportunity to gain live insights and inspiration from a GSoC winner. Get tailored strategies, insider tips for winning proposals, and real-life inspiration for kicking off your GSoC journey with the right guidance.

title: Who is organizing this event?
content: The event is organized by FEDKIIT and features a GSoC alumnus sharing their expertise on how to take active participation in Google Summer of Code.

title: When and where will the event be held?
content: The webinar will be conducted online on 10th January. Join us from the comfort of your home or hostel and get ready to learn directly from a GSoC alumnus.
